// ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ ETADisplay Component ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ
export const ETADisplay = ({ eta = 8, distance = '3.8 km', vehicleId = 'AMB-23', type = 'medical' }) => {
  const [seconds, setSeconds] = useState(eta * 60);
  const accentColor = type === 'fire' ? '#ff2d78' : '#00f5ff';
  const accentRGB = type === 'fire' ? '255,45,120' : '0,245,255';

  useEffect(() => {
    if (seconds <= 0) return;
    const interval = setInterval(() => setSeconds(s => Math.max(0, s - 1)), 1000);
    return () => clearInterval(interval);
  }, []);

  const mins = Math.floor(seconds / 60);
  const secs = seconds % 60;

  return (
    <div style={{
      padding: '20px',
      background: `linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(${accentRGB},0.05) 0%, rgba(4,9,15,0.9) 100%)`,
      border: `1px solid rgba(${accentRGB},0.25)`,
      borderRadius: '8px',
      display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', gap: '20px',
    }}>
      <div style={{ textAlign: 'center' }}>
        <div style={{
          fontFamily: "'Share Tech Mono', monospace",
          fontSize: '52px', fontWeight: '700',
          color: accentColor,
          letterSpacing: '-2px',
          textShadow: `0 0 20px rgba(${accentRGB},0.6)`,
          lineHeight: 1,
        }}>
          {String(mins).padStart(2, '0')}:{String(secs).padStart(2, '0')}
        </div>
        <div style={{
          fontSize: '10px', color: '#5a7a9a', letterSpacing: '2px',
          textTransform: 'uppercase', fontFamily: "'Exo 2', sans-serif", marginTop: '4px',
        }}>
          ETA COUNTDOWN
        </div>
      </div>

      <div style={{ flex: 1, display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column', gap: '10px' }}>
        {[
          { label: 'Vehicle ID', value: vehicleId, color: accentColor },
          { label: 'Distance', value: distance, color: '#7fff00' },
          { label: 'Status', value: 'EN ROUTE', color: '#7fff00' },
        ].map(item => (
          <div key={item.label} style={{
            display: 'flex', justifyContent: 'space-between', alignItems: 'center',
            paddingBottom: '8px',
            borderBottom: '1px solid rgba(0,245,255,0.06)',
          }}>
            <span style={{
              fontSize: '11px', color: '#5a7a9a', letterSpacing: '1.5px',
              textTransform: 'uppercase', fontFamily: "'Exo 2', sans-serif",
            }}>
              {item.label}
            </span>
            <span style={{
              fontFamily: "'Share Tech Mono', monospace",
              fontSize: '14px', color: item.color, fontWeight: '700',
            }}>
              {item.value}
            </span>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  );
};

